    DO NOTE LESSON 1: HELLO WORLD
    DO NOTE
    DO NOTE This program outputs the number 42.
    DO NOTE Watch .1 in the variables panel as you step.
    DO NOTE
    DO NOTE In INTERCAL, READ OUT prints a number.
    DO NOTE Yes, READ OUT writes. WRITE IN reads.
    DO NOTE That is the first of many surprises.

    PLEASE DO .1 <- #42
    DO READ OUT .1
    PLEASE GIVE UP
